text: Kemmental is a municipality of the district of Kreuzlingen in the canton of Thurgau in Switzerland. ==History== The municipality was created on January 1, 1996 by mergxer of the formar municipalities of Alterswilen, Altishausen, Ellighausen, Lippoldswilen, Neuwilen, Siegershausen, Dotnacht and Hugelshofen. ==Images== File:Hugelshofen preghejo 298.JPG|Church of Hugelshofen File:Dotnacht 313.JPG|Dotnacht ==References== Category:Municipalities in Kreuzlingen
title: Kemmental
